                    <p>Croatia Airlines is the flag carrier airline of Croatia owned by the state. It serves domestic & international services mainly to European destinations & has headquarters in Buzin near Zagreb. Apart from the excellent customer service, the airline is known to ease the process to cancel your flight & claim the booking value before the scheduled departure. </p>
                    <p>If you have plans to book flight tickets from Croatia Airlines, make sure you check the ongoing offers & deals, flight booking, & cancellation policy. For your ease, below is an overview of <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/croatia-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Croatia Airlines’ cancellation policy</a>.</p>
